Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.75,0:23:07.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无重力的暗阎　唯有摸索前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.34,0:23:10.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic}Where do we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.63,0:23:19.39,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同莫比乌斯环一般　命运九转轮回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.39,0:23:22.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0.1}Win, Lose Or Draw
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.10,0:23:28.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真实究竟何在{\fnMS Gothic}？ {\fsp0}Lies & Truth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.52,0:23:34.43,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光影回转{\fsp-9}　{\fsp1.5}阴阳相生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:39.39,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运之骰一经掷出　就已无法停止转动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.66,0:23:42.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0}Dive into the Light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.20,0:23:50.79,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭之风扬　我只欲逆风直上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.79,0:23:53.72,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你紧紧拥入怀抱中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.13,0:24:01.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制裁之剑{\fsp-9}　{\fsp1.5}斩断这一昏暗的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.81,0:24:08.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独彷徨　{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0}Lost In Space
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【Main】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.30,0:01:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利他…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.31,0:01:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利行踪不明？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了吗 方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.28,0:01:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利？他是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.78,0:02:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(500,295)\fad(500,500)\fs90\bord4}英雄的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}惑星艾曼塔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}惑星エーメンタール
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惑星艾曼塔采取民主政治
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.28,0:02:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经济状况也很稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.17,0:02:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.17,0:02:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ファン・ヒューリック
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能做得再好点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个真是好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.94,0:02:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰马黛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有吗 真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.48,0:02:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂一个宇宙港居然连马黛都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾曼塔也堕落了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}莉拉·佛罗伦兹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}リラ・フローレンツ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然被你发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我天生小家子气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打从心底不相信幸运和美女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这想法还真是可悲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃一堑长一智嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.91,0:03:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没从失恋中走出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要把我交给警察吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个想去的地方 带我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚来不久 人生地不熟的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个星球的时间流动太缓慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.37,0:03:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藩王殿下对全宇宙有令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓捕逃亡者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(150,0)}亚瑟斯·泰坦尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(150,0)\fs62\fnms gothic}アルセス・タイタニア伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃亡者？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里就是职业介绍所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾曼塔还真是名不虚传啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你一副格格不入的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是个无业游民嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.79,0:04:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.53,0:04:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你从哪儿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾里亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你犯什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打赢了不该赢的仗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我怀疑起整个世道来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是赌徒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说你身怀绝艺？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位高手 请问你杀了多少人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十万人左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你能找到好工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说我还没问你叫什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉·佛罗伦兹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修利先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有惑星工学技术鉴定资格吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你持有什么特殊资格吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:05:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般资格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:06:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙船驾驶执照算吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等级呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.58,0:06:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B级
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B级…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A级都已经不稀奇了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是特A级的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手头倒是有一打求人告示
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去考好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里考？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你已经不用工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.97,0:06:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你联络了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你陪我们走一趟吧 方修利提督
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯卿出任近卫军司令官了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 为了嘉奖他在先前的典礼上为皇帝尽忠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为皇帝尽忠？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听来有点刺耳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(150,0)}哲力胥·泰坦尼亚公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(150,0)\fs62\fnms gothic}ザーリッシュ・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯 忘记了泰坦尼亚一族荣耀的蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青史留名的不会是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.41,0:07:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟斯吗 什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 看到我这张脸就来气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很忙 没事的话就挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开公事不断的天城
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也像我这样来边境忙里偷闲一下怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾曼塔才不是什么边境呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我说 我抓到逃亡者了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:07:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你抓到那家伙了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.32,0:08:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好 亚瑟斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 哥哥的仕途也能更进一步了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.14,0:08:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会亲自押送他去天城
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此为契机 我也向那边…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上派人过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮 亚瑟斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.07,0:08:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过后再联络
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥无论如何都要把我困在这个边境小国里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ament Devil
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.37,0:08:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是食肉鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.58,0:09:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要抓我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你从故乡逃出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市长这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他本人倒是把责任推得一干二净
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管其中有什么原委
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现身于艾曼塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我 亚瑟斯·泰坦尼亚抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修连 听说你打败了泰坦尼亚的舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本来是罪该万死的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但亚术曼藩王殿下愿意对你网开一面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入泰坦尼亚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你今后能为泰坦尼亚贡献才干
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你该不会有什么不满吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样已经是天恩浩荡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.72,0:10:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个提议应该不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正愁找不到工作 本该感激涕零的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却有点 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你确实赢了泰坦尼亚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.82,0:10:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不会有第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.55,0:10:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说那纯属巧合吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚可以输给天才
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却决不能凑巧失败
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修连
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有选择权
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺泰坦尼亚则生 逆泰坦尼亚则死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若选择前者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚会分给你丰厚的财富和无边的权势
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.61,0:11:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若选择后者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚会赐你华丽的一死 用宝石之泪埋葬你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你要选哪一个 方修连？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.47,0:11:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.38,0:11:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类可以分成两类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配者和受支配者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只是个下级官吏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道就不想成为支配方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你这话就不对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了支配者和受支配者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有第三种人类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌受人支配的一类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.86,0:11:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修连
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵阁下 我可不记得自己改过名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不叫修连 我的名字是方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想拉人入伙的话 好歹得记住对方的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你选择哪一方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我选择远离泰坦尼亚的生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我答应你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.06,0:12:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个提议毕竟不错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接受你的建议
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薪水和带薪休假的事宜可以今后正式谈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我先答应了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是发自内心的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.11,0:12:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这人不会撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你虽然长得不错 但不是我喜欢的那一型
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么今天就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他永远都是少年的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:13:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样才配做王侯的从者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚一族都必须遵从藩王殿下的旨意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修连卿 我会待你以上宾之礼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说 今后还请多多关照啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上叫人准备房间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我住不惯你们的洋房
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有小旅馆住就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得很有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送修连卿出门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来脑袋暂时是保住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 接下来要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:13:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边请
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 提督
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄关不是在对面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.39,0:14:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才叫我「提督」？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能把你交给泰坦尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车子在对面 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 给我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.68,0:14:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底是什么人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你决不能屈服于泰坦尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我们一起逃吧 方修利提督
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个 不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这当口逃走的话 我就不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我们的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.79,0:14:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄必须当好英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别磨蹭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.53,0:14:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上划出警戒线
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.56,0:15:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到抵抗格杀勿论
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来就没必要保护那家伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是没办法的事呢 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.37,0:15:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没发现的话 就去附近找
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跑不远 给我搜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.25,0:15:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到抵抗的话 杀无赦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等什么呢 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾曼塔也有这种地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论在哪里 都有被命运抛弃的人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为藏身之地再合适不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那些人是你的同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些拼上性命断了我后路的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用装了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.62,0:16:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本来就是冲我来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你特意带我去找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果却被泰坦尼亚抢了先
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是卡萨比安卡公国的遗臣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萨比安卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被泰坦尼亚毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在三十年以前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要救我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了复兴我们的故国
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是唯一一个曾战胜过泰坦尼亚的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.43,0:16:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你大旗一挥 同志自会蜂拥而至
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能协助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:16:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我们的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.43,0:17:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有一个目的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「没有泰坦尼亚的宇宙」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有泰坦尼亚的宇宙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.73,0:17:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想法不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算泰坦尼亚消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一定会有替代者登场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要复仇是你的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但实际上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多数人都在泰坦尼亚的统治下安居乐业
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不惜与他们为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是花时间推动意识改革呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这方面重新想一想怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.65,0:17:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随遇而安啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你会被杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在这里还不是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追兵很快就会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想失去你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.65,0:18:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说倒是蛮帅的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.40,0:18:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也还不想死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人总会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你绝对会死 没有活路的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.43,0:18:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.67,0:18:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算你狠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用做到这个地步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.02,0:18:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杂草这东西若不去管 就会无限滋生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(150,0)}伊德里斯·泰坦尼亚公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(150,0)\fs62\fnms gothic}イドリス・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除恶务尽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}维尔达纳帝国皇帝 哈鲁夏六世
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ヴァルダナ帝国皇帝 ハルシャ六世
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作为维尔达纳帝国近卫军司令官
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有责任保护陛下周全
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚历亚伯特卿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.36,0:19:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听说了吗 褚士朗卿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯卿一事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肃清吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说沙洛蒙一派确实提出了抗议
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他居然全员处刑 太大胆了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于帝国来说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚本来就是个威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此事为契机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛乱份子恐怕会人数暴涨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}亚历亚伯特·泰坦尼亚公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}アリアバート・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.55,0:19:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防民之口 甚于防川
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藩王殿下为什么要举荐伊德里斯卿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}褚士朗·泰坦尼亚公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ジュスラン・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下并不是信赖伊德里斯卿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是投下了一枚石子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波纹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下恐怕是想观察水波成何走势
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.99,0:19:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都是殿下的棋子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.64,0:20:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是殿下喜欢的马黛茶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}无地藩王 亚术曼·泰坦尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}無地藩王 アジュマーン・タイタニア
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平持续得太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平持续得越长越好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路途若是过于平坦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.03,0:20:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人会不觉间变得迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了坑坑洼洼的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等跌跟头的时候就晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没什么文化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法体会这一比喻的深意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.21,0:20:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但藩王殿下似乎在为泰坦尼亚的未来而忧心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.31,0:20:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 到底怎么样啊 好不好吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.19,0:20:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一份
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:21:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶在卡萨比安卡公国时代曾当过王妃的侍女哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.33,0:21:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？那是多少万年前的事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.98,0:21:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王妃大人喜欢吃果酱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每天都用从庭院里采摘的新鲜丁香果做给她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丁香果压得太碎会发苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.49,0:21:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碾压的时候要格外小心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.19,0:21:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉 蛋包饭还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听奶奶说啊 你这家伙真没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.87,0:21:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉 有人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 来就来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.61,0:21:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫来就来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是泰坦尼亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.46,0:21:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴·鲍尔 这人就是传说中的提督
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.94,0:21:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(573,923)\fad(500,500)}佛罗利蒙德·戴·鲍尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.94,0:21:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(573,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}フロリモンド・デ・ボーア
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.09,0:21:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.98,0:22:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是戴·鲍尔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会给你看一样好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.39,0:22:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.50,0:22:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.28,0:22:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.65,0:22:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.90,0:22:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.51,0:22:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.99,0:22:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利提督首次亲眼目睹泰坦尼亚家族
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.92,0:24:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.44,0:24:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是他们害我不得安生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.48,0:24:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄这玩意真不好当
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.90,0:24:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次又要当这些可疑家伙的同伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.03,0:24:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(652,290)\fad(500,0)\fs90\bord5}莉拉的决心


